errors.name: ClientError
errors.description: Represents all the errors related to the GraphQL client.

errors.name: ConnectionError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred in client while connecting with the GraphQL server.

errors.name: DuplicateOperationError
errors.description: Represents an error where multiple operations with the same name exists

errors.name: Error
errors.description: Represents any error related to the Ballerina GraphQL module

errors.name: ExecutionError
errors.description: Represents the errors occurred while executing a GraphQL document

errors.name: FieldNotFoundError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred when a required field not found in graphql service resources

errors.name: InitializationError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred in client while creating the GraphQL client.

errors.name: InvalidArgumentTypeError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred when the provided argument type mismatched with the expected type

errors.name: InvalidDocumentError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred when a required field not found in graphql service resources

errors.name: InvalidSelectionError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred when the provided selection is invalid

errors.name: ListenerError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred while a listener operation

errors.name: MissingRequiredArgumentError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred when a required argument is missing

errors.name: NotImplementedError
errors.description: Represents a non-implemented feature error

errors.name: NotSupportedError
errors.description: Represents an unsupported functionality error

errors.name: OperationNotFoundError
errors.description: Represents an error where the provided operation is not found in a document

errors.name: ParsingError
errors.description: Represents an error occurred while parsing a document

errors.name: ValidationError
errors.description: Represents the errors occurred while validating a GraphQL document
